title: dal

needs:
- 2 cloves garlic, diced
- 1 shallot or quarter onion, diced
- sesame oil
- 50g lentils
- 200ml water
- stock
- 50g lentils
- ginger
- cinnamon
- salt
- pepper

steps:
- fry the garlic and onion in the oil.
- add the water, stock, and lentils.
- add a dash of ginger, cinnamon, salt, and pepper.
- stew for 20 minutes, or until tasty.
